      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.hIhgdXnqGHBm0A64]{Envoy Improvisation}</p>\n<p>&nbsp;@Icon[type:language-dependent] Language-dependent @Icon[type:mind-affecting] Mind-Affecting @Icon[type:sense-dependent] Sense-Dependent</p>\n<p>Whenever you or an ally deal damage to an opponent within 60 feet of you, you can take a reaction to allow all allies within 60 feet of the opponent to take a guarded step as a reaction. All of the characters who took a guarded step using this improvisation have their speed reduced by 5 feet until the end of their next turn.</p>"
